# qt-251: package-lock.json is gitignored because this repo lives inside
# the behavioral-contracts pnpm workspace during local dev. `npm install`
# in that context produces a lockfile that references workspace-relative
# paths (../../behavioral-contracts-saas/node_modules/.pnpm/...) which
# break `npm ci` in CI. Re-resolving against package.json on every CI run
# is the cost of the workspace setup.
package-lock.json
